  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Shop Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for one customer-friendly, result-driven and reliable Shop Manager to be responsible for all shop duties from customer greetings to cashing sales as well as inventory management and shop keeping for our outlet at IMM.<br /><br />We do provide training to understand our Brand and our selling process, detailed product descriptions to help with the sales and induction to our POS and communication tools.</p><p>Main responsibilities are:</p><ul><li>Welcoming customers, understanding their expectations and assisting them in selecting and purchasing the relevant products to their needs by providing relevant and accurate product recommendations.</li><li>Upholding general store housekeeping including the tidiness of the store and the display of attractive Visual Merchandising, cashiering, tallying sales reports, opening and closing of POS.</li><li>Managing stock inventory, including regular stock checks and stocktakes.</li></ul><p><br />Requirements:</p><ul><li>Good working experience and proven in retail sales</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li> A friendly and energetic personality with customer service focus</li><li>Availability to work flexible shifts including some week-ends</li><li>Proficiency in English</li><li>Fluent in Mandarin is a plus in order to answer queries from Mandarin speaking customers</li><li>Singaporean/Permanent resident only</li></ul><p>Please apply now to be considered for the role and send your resume.<br /><br />We will only contact shortlisted candidates.</p>",
